male illustrated in the figures 9–10 is from 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:BC0E87DAB564DB786CD7B641FE6BFF35:31786017B564DB796E06B6B1FCC0FA8C" box="[582,775,1220,1245]" country="Brazil" county="Km" municipality="Senador Guiomard" name="Reserva Catuaba" pageId="6" pageNumber="469" stateProvince="Acre">Reserva Catuaba</location>
, 
